channel.title: [Request] 503 Server and/or 503 XTEA Keys [Request]
channel.description: Well, I'm sorry about posting this here, but requests are forbidden in the server downloads section, and this is kind of a help thread. I'm looking for a 503 server, or the XTEA keys from the mapdata folder in the server. I've searched through all the results from searching for 503 on here, and on Rune-Serber. If anyone has what I'm looking for, please upload it and post here. It would be greatly appreciated.

item.title: [Request] 503 Server and/or 503 XTEA Keys [Request]
item.dc:creator: @death23 death23
item.description:
@death23 wrote:

[quote=“Native^, post:2, topic:438150”]I believe the 508 keys are the same, and will also work.
And for the server. I think you’ll only have to change the login protocol of a 508 server. Updating and stuff is the same I believe.[/quote]

He’s looking for 503-specific keys. He knows that 508’ll work but if someone in their computer has a 503 key store it might have some regions that 503 didn’t and he’s using it for a use other than a 503 server.

If people could just look through their computers really quickly and see if they have a 503 server with some mapdata and to just upload it to uppit or something and post a link here it would be greatly appreciated.
